originalText.text: Donna helped me immensely during difficult time in my life. With every session I was feeling more confidence and understanding what I was searching for.  Donna knows how to help her clients to focus on important issues and create better vision. With love and compassion she shows the way to happier life.

originalText.text: Donna's advice with dating help was amazing. By one simple change in perspective I was able to turn things around and stopped doing the things that turned my love interest off. To my great surprise the next thing I knew they started pursuing me. She profiled my love interest's intimacy style from her book The Passion Principle and it worked! I knew what they needed to open up and get close. Now I'm in the driver's seat and I love it! It really works, fast, thoroughly and effectively!

originalText.text: Donna is an exceptional coach and therapist. She has an uncanny ability to understand your situation and background after only a few minutes of conversation. Her advice and analysis is powerful, practical and can be life changing. I've met with her alone and with another family member and she excels in both types of sessions. Highly recommend her to anyone wanting to make a change in their life.

originalText.text: Donna LeBlanc is a master shadow working, powerful, intuitive therapist.  She has written several books and helped my former partner and I separate our romantic relationship and continue our  working relationship.  It has been a difficult process and I am so grateful to have Donna on both our sides.
